reviews.review_text:
fxck the soundboard I love this show.

But the Charlie Miller boards mix out the Brent in a totally fxcked up way.  Listen to the Terrapin outro.  End of story.

Take a Listen I had the second set of this show on tape the whole time I follwed the Dead in the late 80's. I listened to it so many times it is now part of my DNA. I promise you it's worth a listen.  Be patient. It unfolds like a comfy psychedelic blanket. It feels like home to me now.  Enjoy!
Terrapin I taped this show with Senn 441s from the front row of tapers section. No cut on terrapin
